actually very well said, but one small flaw in this. China has for many years killed their own people, Excecuted the Political opposition. Also China did unspeakable things to the Burmese people, as well as the Taiwanese.<br>
<br>
<br>
ok i have ranted way to much on this. and appologize if i have stepped on anyones shoes. I just wanted to toss a Europeans point of view in this debate.<br>
